        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sum _{i=1}^{n}f(a+ih)\,\Delta x.}
  As this computation is carried out for each 
  
    
      
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle n}
  , the new function is defined at the points:

  
    
      
        a
        ,
        a
        +
        h
        ,
        a
        +
        2
