        ,
        a
        +
        i
        h
        ]
        
          
            )
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \left(\sum g\right)\!(a+nh)=\sum _{i=1}^{n}g{\big (}[a+(i-1)h,a+ih]{\big )}.}
  These are their properties:

Constant rule: If 
  
    
      
        c
      
    
    {\displaystyle c}
   is a constant, then
  
    
      
