    {\displaystyle (v_{0},\dots ,{\widehat {v_{i}}},\dots ,v_{k})}
  is the 
  
    
      
        i
      
    
    {\displaystyle i}
  th face of 
  
    
      
        σ
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sigma }
  , obtained by deleting its 
  
    
      
