    {\displaystyle C_{k}}
  , elements of the subgroup

  
    
      
        
          Z
          
            k
          
        
        =
        ker
        ⁡
        
          ∂
          
            k
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle Z_{k}=\ker \partial _{k}}
  are referred to as cycles, and the subgroup

  
    
      
        
