        ,
        
          d
          
            B
            ,
            ∗
          
        
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle (B_{*},d_{B,*})}
   is a sequence 
  
    
      
        
          f
          
            ∗
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle f_{*}}
   of homomorphisms 
  
    
      
        
          f
          
            n
          
        
        :
        
          A
          
