    {\displaystyle n}
   that commutes with the boundary operators on the two chain complexes, so 
  
    
      
        
          d
          
            B
            ,
            n
          
        
        ∘
        
          f
          
            n
          
        
        =
        
          f
          
            n
            −
            1
          
        
        ∘
        
          d
          
